```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Game {
        +canvas
        +ctx
        +data: DataRegistry
        +sound: SoundManager
        +input: InputManager
        +platform: PlatformBridge
        +fsm: StateMachine
        +run: RunContext
        +init() Promise
        +start() void
        +transitionTo(state) void
    }

    class StateMachine {
        -_current
        -_next
        +set(state)
        +update(dt)
        +render(ctx)
        +handleInput(ev)
    }

    class RunContext {
        +balance: number
        +heatmap: HeatmapTracker
        +chips: ChipManager
        +lastSpinNumber: number
        +lastSpinPayout: number
        +history: number[]
    }

    class DataRegistry {
        -_bets
        -_wheel
        -_chips
        -_config
        +load(basePath) Promise
        +getBets() Map
        +getWheelOrder() number[]
        +getChipDefs() array
        +getConfig() object
    }

    class BetResolver {
        +SELECTORS: Map
        +resolve(spinNumber, bets) ResolutionResult
        +matches(betDef, instance, n) bool
    }

    class WheelPhysics {
        -_state
        +start(targetNumber, spinConfig)
        +update(dt)
        +getBallAngle() number
        +getWheelAngle() number
        +isSettled() bool
    }

    class ChipManager {
        -_placedBets: array
        -_lastBets: array
        +place(typeId, numbers, amount)
        +clear()
        +rebet()
        +totalWagered() number
    }

    class HeatmapTracker {
        -_history: number[]
        -_counts: Map
        +record(n)
        +getHotNumbers(k) number[]
        +getColdNumbers(k) number[]
    }

    class IGameState {
        <<interface>>
        +enter()
        +exit()
        +update(dt)
        +render(ctx)
        +handleInput(ev)
    }

    Game --* DataRegistry
    Game --* StateMachine
    Game --* SoundManager
    Game --* InputManager
    Game --* PlatformBridge
    Game --* RunContext
    RunContext --* HeatmapTracker
    RunContext --* ChipManager
    StateMachine --> IGameState
    BettingState ..|> IGameState
    SpinState ..|> IGameState
    RevealState ..|> IGameState
    ResultState ..|> IGameState
    LoadingState ..|> IGameState
    SpinState --* WheelPhysics
    RevealState --> BetResolver
```

# Roulette Architecture Notes

- **Bet selection is data-driven**: `bets.json` lists templates with `selector` keys; `BetResolver.SELECTORS` is a name→function map. No `if/switch` on bet type anywhere.
- **Wheel uses European single-zero** (37 sectors) — order in `wheel.json`.
- **All gameplay numbers** (payouts, spin duration, ball physics) live in JSON; `GameConfig.js` only holds geometry/colors.
- **States separate concerns**:
  - `BettingState`: chip placement, no time pressure, transitions to `SpinState` on "spin".
  - `SpinState`: runs `WheelPhysics`, locks input.
  - `RevealState`: short pause with ball settled, runs `BetResolver`, kicks off VFX.
  - `ResultState`: shows summary overlay, allows rebet/clear/spin again.
